Predict the output (index) produced by the following pseudocode when given A = [1,3,5,7,9], key = 7.
`procedure BSearch(A,n,key)
  low<-1; high<-n;
  while low<=high do
    mid<-(low+high)//2;
    if A[mid]=key then return mid;
    if A[mid]<key then low<-mid+1 else high<-mid-1
  end while
  return -1
end procedure`
